34:02.700 --> 34:03.860
There are places...

34:05.120 --> 34:07.327
discreet places...

34:09.080 --> 34:10.081
that could help you.

34:14.920 --> 34:16.376
I think that's a good idea.

34:17.630 --> 34:19.131
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

34:19.850 --> 34:21.215
Okay.

34:22.930 --> 34:23.919
Come here.

34:33.650 --> 34:37.063
You just gotta let me know you're safe.

34:39.160 --> 34:40.559
