keep doing as you are.

38:54.330 --> 38:55.536
I'll be in touch.

38:56.500 --> 38:57.489
Okay.

39:08.680 --> 39:09.795
Danny.

39:10.890 --> 39:13.381
What happened to you?
The board will be here in a minute.

39:13.560 --> 39:14.595
Oh, um...

39:14.850 --> 39:16.636
Uh. Come on. Come on.

39:24.570 --> 39:26.026
Here. Put this on.

39:26.610 --> 39:27.599
Thanks.

39:36.700 --> 39:39.112
- What's this?
- Those are the files you asked for.

39:40.960 --> 39:44.202
Where's everything else?
All of my father's things?

39:44.380 --> 39:45.790
That's all I could find in storage.

39:46.710 --> 39:48.712
It's been 15 years.
There was probably more,

39:48.880 --> 39:51.838
but things get moved around,
and then, eventually, they get lost.

39:57.140 --> 39:58.175
And forgotten.

40:04.820 --> 40:06.219
Do you think this
is a good company?

40:07.360 --> 40:08.896
To work? Sure.

40:09.530 --> 40:12.021
