40:16.910 --> 40:19.242
- You saw the video, right?
- Yeah.

40:21.370 --> 40:23.076
What did you think?
It's not really my place to say.

40:23.170 --> 40:24.159
Hey.

40:25.000 --> 40:26.035
It's okay.

40:28.420 --> 40:30.297
My mother lives on Staten Island.

40:39.560 --> 40:41.300
