42:02.270 --> 42:03.259
So, I'm standing.

42:03.680 --> 42:06.558
Danny, you may have
a voice on this board,

42:07.350 --> 42:09.056
but it's just a courtesy.

42:09.360 --> 42:12.898
Don't expect anyone here
to be listening to a kid

42:13.070 --> 42:15.447
