from a Himalayan monastery.

42:15.610 --> 42:17.100
Lawrence,
you don't have to attack him.

42:18.450 --> 42:21.738
- Danny's plan is...
- The idiotic dream of a child.

42:24.750 --> 42:26.456
Karen Page at
The Bulletin
