49:01.060 --> 49:02.687
You've been ousted from Rand.

49:57.320 --> 49:59.117
Oh, no...

50:01.490 --> 50:03.287
Radovan. Radovan!

50:05.960 --> 50:07.245
Sabina...

50:07.500 --> 50:10.162
Sabina's fine. She's home.

50:11.340 --> 50:12.910
She's safe.

50:16.680 --> 50:18.170
