Where is she?

50:54.420 --> 50:55.626
Anzhou...

51:03.350 --> 51:04.339
Radovan.

51:08.480 --> 51:10.186
Oh, Danny.

51:14.360 --> 51:15.349
Danny?

51:16.530 --> 51:17.736
Anzhou...

51:21.660 --> 51:23.230
It's the name of a city in China.

51:25.370 --> 51:26.496
Have you been there?

51:28.460 --> 51:31.623
