you might be stopping by.

52:01.780 --> 52:02.815
How did you know?

52:04.240 --> 52:07.243
How did you know

52:07.410 --> 52:09.571
- about the account?
- I always knew.

52:10.620 --> 52:13.168
Did you really think it was that easy
to steal millions of dollars

52:13.330 --> 52:14.706
from the company
and not get caught?

52:15.210 --> 52:17.087
Come on, I thought I raised you
smarter than that.

52:19.920 --> 52:22.047
Who do you think's been keeping
your transactions hidden

52:22.220 --> 52:24.427
from the accountants?
Or the SEC?

52:26.060 --> 52:29.018
Stick with business, son.
You're a shitty thief.

52:32.940 --> 52:33.975
Why?

52:36.940 --> 52:39.067
Why would you let me think
I was getting away with it?

52:39.780 --> 52:42.852
Oh, well, we all have our private vices.
Yours just happened to be embezzling.

52:44.370 --> 52:46.827
And as long as your hobby
didn't interfere with our work...

52:47.540 --> 52:48.609
who was I to judge?

52:50.410 --> 52:54.119
But honestly, Ward,
couldn't you have just gotten a mistress?

52:54.920 --> 52:55.989
Much simpler.

52:56.170 --> 53:00.960
I am sick of it!
The control, the manipulation...

53:01.130 --> 53:02.290
Yeah, I know you're upset.

53:02.470 --> 53:04.961
You don't see it now,
but I had to stop you from leaving.

53:05.640 --> 53:08.256
You were making
the biggest mistake of your life.

53:08.430 --> 53:10.091
That was my money!

53:10.270 --> 53:12.977
Well, technically, it was
the employee pension fund's money.

53:14.190 --> 53:16.260
I was gonna be free.

53:16.480 --> 53:18.220
Yeah, we're all gonna be free, Ward.

53:18.690 --> 53:21.147
We are so close to being
done with the Hand.

53:21.820 --> 53:24.778
Now, if you had run away,
run away like a scared child,

53:24.990 --> 53:27.572
you would have regretted it
every day for the rest of your life.

53:27.830 --> 53:29.286
Now, relax.

53:29.870 --> 53:31.406
You just had a moment of weakness.

53:32.870 --> 53:36.328
It happens.
I'm not gonna punish you for it.

53:39.000 --> 53:41.958
I'm not a child
and I'm not scared.

53:42.130 --> 53:43.506
Well, then stop acting like one.

53:44.550 --> 53:47.542
Today's a good day.
You should be happy.

53:50.890 --> 53:54.348
You know what the last happy day
of my life was, Dad?

53:56.150 --> 53:57.606
The day you died.

54:05.110 --> 54:06.407
That's just mean, Ward.

54:13.620 --> 54:16.418
You should be grateful. Yeah.

54:16.620 --> 54:19.623
You wouldn't have a life without me.
I've given you everything.

54:19.920 --> 54:23.504
